            <lg xml:id="TK239">
<l>vacaiyilā vaṇpayaṉ kuṉṟu micaiyilā</l>
<l>yākkai poṟutta nilam</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The ground which supports a body without fame will diminish in its rich produce.</l>
